# Sprint 001 – Clicker Hero Foundation

## 📅 Duration
Start Date: 03-10-26  
End Date:   03-17-26  
Length: 1 Week  

---

## 🎯 Sprint Goal
Deliver a playable Clicker Hero MVP with:
- Manual click scoring
- Passive income system
- Auto-save every 30 seconds
- Load existing user score from database

---

## 📦 Scope (In Scope)

### Frontend (React + TS)
- [ ] Click button increases score
- [ ] Passive score increment every second (basic)
- [ ] State management structure
- [ ] Auto-save timer
- [ ] Fetch score on mount

### Backend (Laravel)
- [ ] Create ClickerHero model
- [ ] Create migration with foreign key (user_id)
- [ ] Create API route for saving score
- [ ] Create API route for loading score
- [ ] Add validation
- [ ] Protect with auth middleware

---

## 🚫 Out of Scope
- Leaderboards
- Achievements
- Animations
- Sound effects
- Multiple upgrades
- Production performance optimization
- Prestige System
- Percentage Modifiers for passive income

---

## 🏗 Architecture Plan

### Data Model
ClickerHero Table:
- id
- user_id (foreign key)
- score
- prestige_level
- updated_at

### API Structure
POST /api/clicker/save  
GET /api/clicker/load  

---

## 🧪 Definition of Done

- Score persists after refresh
- No console errors
- No database errors
- Clean merge into main
- Deployed to production
- Works on mobile

---

## 🔄 CI/CD Plan
- Feature branch: feature/clicker-hero
- Merge to main after completion
- Run deployment script
- Verify production
- Tag release v1.1.0 (Optional)

